# Pre-rendered Windows icon checked into the repo so Windows CI builds
# don't need to install an SVG renderer (rsvg-convert / cairosvg are
# painful on Windows). Re-render this from master.svg on a machine that
# has rsvg-convert by running `python generate.py` and committing the
# updated file.
!windows/
windows/*
!windows/app.ico
